  14 Aug 2010; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@aidecoe.name>
  genkernel-9999.ebuild:
  - Put 'dosed' in pkg_preinst instead of 'sed -i' in src_install.
  - Info about bug report in pkg_postinst.

  12 Aug 2010; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@aidecoe.name> +metadata.xml,
  genkernel-9999.ebuild:
  Removed src_unpack and moved the relevant line into src_install.

  11 Aug 2010; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@aidecoe.name>
  +genkernel-9999.ebuild, +files/genkernel.bash:
  Ebuild is copied from the main Portage tree and completely rewritten by me.

  Shortly:
    - use my fork of Genkernel
    - depend on >=dracut-007
    - install bash-completion script only if bash-completion USE flag is
      enabled
    - removed download of additional packages since Dracut takes required
      things from the system
    - using ebuild functions instead of cp

  See ChangeLog in Portage tree for full history of Genkernel ebuilds.
